      "amount": "2 tbsp, chopped",
      "notes": "optional garnish"
    }
  ],
  "instructions": [
    "Heat olive oil in a large pot over medium heat.",
    "Add diced onion and sauté until translucent.",
    "Stir in minced garlic, cumin, smoked paprika, and oregano for 30 seconds.",
    "Add basmati rice and toast until lightly browned.",
    "Fold in chickpeas, tomato paste, and sherry vinegar.",
    "Pour in vegetable broth, season with salt and pepper, and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce heat, cover, and simmer for 25 minutes until rice is tender and liquid absorbed.",
    "Stir in chopped parsley and adjust seasoning if needed.",
    "Fluff the pilaf with a fork before serving."
